        {
            "id": 6020116,
            "title": "台積貼息台股挫逾百點 三大法人賣超22.23億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (12) 日受台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 除息失靈貼息影響，一度下跌逾 200 點，加上電子、金融權值股疲弱，指數開低走低震盪，終場收 22,287.82 點，下跌 182.28 點或 0.81%，成交量略縮為 3,386.22 億元；三大法人合計賣超 22.23 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020116%2Fl%2F72494fb3d90677ae75288455e1781e8c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台積貼息台股挫逾百點 三大法人賣超22.23億元。(圖:鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察三大法人今天籌碼動向，外資買超 2.67 億元；自營商買超 3.9 億元；投信賣超 28.79 億元；三大法人合計賣超 22.23 億元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
